msgid "| Input | Source | Purpose |"
msgstr "| 输入 | 来源 | 用途 |"

msgid "| Device type | Strategy | Reason |"
msgstr "| 设备类型 | 策略 | 原因 |"

msgid "| Role | CPUs |"
msgstr "| 角色 | CPU |"

msgid ""
"| Worker | Logical NPU | CPU pool | IRQ CPUs | Main CPUs | ACL CPU | Release"
" CPU |"
msgstr "| 工作进程 | 逻辑NPU | CPU池 | IRQ CPU | 主CPU | ACL CPU | 释放CPU |"

msgid "| Process | Visible NPU | Final CPU pool |"
msgstr "| 进程 | 可见NPU | 最终CPU池 |"

msgid ""
"| Allowed CPUs | `/proc/self/status` `Cpus_allowed_list` | The only CPUs "
"eligible for binding. Container cpusets are respected. |"
msgstr ""
"| 允许的CPU | `/proc/self/status` `Cpus_allowed_list` | "
"唯一可绑定的CPU。容器cpuset设置会被尊重。 |"

msgid ""
"| Logical NPU map | `npu-smi info -m` | Maps card/chip IDs to global logical"
" NPU IDs and gives `total_logic_npus`. On Ascend 950, `Chip Logic ID` is not"
" reported, so `NPU ID` is used as the logical ID. |"
msgstr ""
"| 逻辑NPU映射 | `npu-smi info -m` | 将卡/芯片ID映射到全局逻辑NPU "
"ID，并给出`total_logic_npus`。在Ascend 950上，不报告`Chip Logic ID`，因此使用`NPU ID`作为逻辑ID。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| Running NPUs | `npu-smi info` process table, filtered by "
"`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` | Identifies the logical NPUs used by this "
"worker process. A2/A3 process rows use `NPU Chip`; Ascend 950 process rows "
"use `NPU ID`. |"
msgstr ""
"| 运行中的NPU | `npu-smi info`进程表，经`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`过滤 | "
"标识此工作进程使用的逻辑NPU。A2/A3进程行使用`NPU Chip`；Ascend 950进程行使用`NPU ID`。 |"

msgid ""
"| Topology affinity | `npu-smi info -t topo` | Provides NPU-to-CPU affinity "
"for `topo_affinity` mode. |"
msgstr ""
"| 拓扑亲和性 | `npu-smi info -t topo` | 为`topo_affinity`模式提供NPU到CPU的亲和性信息。 |"

msgid ""
"| CPU NUMA map | `lscpu -e=CPU,NODE` | Used to extend single-NUMA affinity "
"pools to the next NUMA node. |"
msgstr "| CPU NUMA映射 | `lscpu -e=CPU,NODE` | 用于将单NUMA亲和性池扩展到下一个NUMA节点。 |"

msgid ""
"| A3 | `global_slice` | A3 uses HCCS card-to-card interconnect. Each NPU is "
"nearly equidistant from all NUMA nodes, so there is no strong NPU-to-NUMA "
"affinity signal. Global logical NPU ID based slicing gives deterministic, "
"non-overlapping CPU pools and CPU/NUMA isolation between workers. |"
msgstr ""
"| A3 | `global_slice` | "
"A3使用HCCS卡间互联。每个NPU与所有NUMA节点的距离几乎相等，因此没有强烈的NPU到NUMA亲和性信号。基于全局逻辑NPU "
"ID的分片提供确定性的、不重叠的CPU池以及工作进程间的CPU/NUMA隔离。 |"

msgid ""
"| Ascend 950 | `global_slice` | Ascend 950 reports NPU-to-NPU/NIC topology "
"but does not report NPU-to-CPU affinity in `npu-smi info -t topo`. It also "
"reports process rows by `NPU ID` instead of `NPU Chip`. Global logical NPU "
"ID based slicing keeps CPU pools deterministic without relying on missing "
"affinity data. |"
msgstr ""
"| Ascend 950 | `global_slice` | Ascend 950报告NPU到NPU/NIC的拓扑，但不报告`npu-smi info"
" -t topo`中的NPU到CPU亲和性。它还通过`NPU ID`而非`NPU Chip`报告进程行。基于全局逻辑NPU "
"ID的分片使CPU池保持确定性，无需依赖缺失的亲和性数据。 |"

msgid ""
"| A2 and Atlas 300 inference products | `topo_affinity` | A2 and Atlas 300 "
"inference products provide NPU-to-CPU affinity information through `npu-smi "
"info -t topo`, so they use this topology signal when available. |"
msgstr ""
"| A2和Atlas 300推理产品 | `topo_affinity` | A2和Atlas 300推理产品通过`npu-smi info -t "
"topo`提供NPU到CPU的亲和性信息，因此在可用时会使用此拓扑信号。 |"

